dct_title_s: Planos callejeros de Málaga y Playa del Palo = Málaga y Playa del Palo, roteiro = Málaga, Playa del Palo street map = Málaga, Playa del Palo, Stadtplan = Málaga, Playa del Palo, plan des rues
dct_description_sm: Panel title. At head of title on panel: RACE. "© Editorial Everest, S.A." On cover: Escala plano callejero de Málaga 1:10,000. Escala plano callejero de Playa de Palo 1:11,000. Map is continued on verso. Includes indexes, illustration, and list of abbreviations. "Depósito legal: LE: 277-2010." North oriented to top right.
